description:
FunkeyPay is a new marketing solution for Person-to-Person (P2P) payment on Social Networking Service (SNS) platforms.

FunKeyPay is currently working on “V-solution”, a marketing solution based on standard API provided by SNS, and “G-Payment”, a business developed based on global payment solution. Also, FunKeyPay strives to provide better convenience with the ultimate goal of providing service that combines “V-Solution” and “G-Payment”.
name: FunKeyPay
